[normal]so published on our
[normal] website
[normal] and include 
[normal]              
[normal]main 
[normal]roads, bus routes and roads leading to fire stations and hospitals, etc.  
[normal]              
[normal]Pavements 
[normal]in busy areas will also be treat
[normal]ed to help pedestrians and support 
[normal]              
[normal]local businesses.  A pan-London Strategic Salt Reserve is also available for 
[normal]              
[normal]us and the boroughs shoul
[normal]d supplies become low during the winter.
