[normal] detailed plans for grit/salt requirements, based on past experience. The main use is around stations, but depot walkways 
[normal]and external paths around office accommodation
[normal] are treated
[normal]. 
[normal]Grit 
[normal]orders are 
[normal]placed in August/September each year. On the platforms 
[normal]‘
[normal]Killfrost
[normal]’
[normal] is also used
[normal] and the required supplies have been ordered. 
